{"tid":1800687,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【G20全球登報半年誌】","createTime":"2019-12-28T05:20:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T13:03:49.000Z","uid":240362,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76ef2148f1b419abd388ee2990c4ad1f04c52e6a","tid":1800687,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/80749852_446490162692807_7603063699946864640_o.jpg?_nc_cat=108&amp;_nc_eui2=AeEgjJ88l4nktH3KxOSUFG3k1aFgjWWBB9t3TR2AVcP4vPfZ0NhGi69sbzzFSJRyUhFlSAK1osR7DF9tsqjuYrak3fDkvnQdHPQwtlTpMaIIqQ&amp;_nc_ohc=GlhDnW56dUgAQmADbQqIjSAyOgXJ4kReifeuiK2xe16LZyOPwyzvQBd6Q&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=314c2c25cd4a08c8c8f14e577af4a085&amp;oe=5EB24C15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F80749852_446490162692807_7603063699946864640_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D108%26_nc_eui2%3DAeEgjJ88l4nktH3KxOSUFG3k1aFgjWWBB9t3TR2AVcP4vPfZ0NhGi69sbzzFSJRyUhFlSAK1osR7DF9tsqjuYrak3fDkvnQdHPQwtlTpMaIIqQ%26_nc_ohc%3DGlhDnW56dUgAQmADbQqIjSAyOgXJ4kReifeuiK2xe16LZyOPwyzvQBd6Q%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D314c2c25cd4a08c8c8f14e577af4a085%26oe%3D5EB24C15&h=158779a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Fight for Freedom, Stand with Hong Kong」.<br />\n<br />\n今天是大阪G20峰會舉行的半週年，也是我們FHK團隊登報事成的半週年。香港人的抗爭，已經超過了二百日。<br />\n<br />\n這半年以來，團隊以全球登報為號召發起了兩次(628、101)眾籌，期間還有一次與攬炒團隊的合作(819)，有賴各位港人的厚愛，三次眾籌先後籌得了約三千萬港元的募款。憑藉這次史無前例的眾籌計劃、以及於一天內籌獲近七百萬的驚人速度，香港贏得了全球媒體的大舉關注。<br />\n<br />\nNHK主播在大阪峰會現場報導的鏡頭前高舉「Stand with Hong Kong at G20」的廣告標語、得到現代語言學泰斗Noam Chomsky來函支持、還有全球各地多處自發舉行的快閃聲援集會，紛紛成為香港人的里程碑，自此掀起了國際社會的波瀾，各國傳媒均增派記者駐港採訪我們香港人的若水之夏。<br />\n<br />\n後來就如同大家所知的，美國火速通過了擱置多時的《香港人權民主法案》。法案背後，當然絕不止我們團隊的努力，有包括眾志、HKIAD、攬炒團隊在內等每個致力開拓國際戰線的組織，還有為香港浴血的每位手足，每滴血淚，都鑄成了香港人的道標。<br />\n<br />\n但抗爭尚未完結，這半年甚至很可能只是遙遙長路的開端。本地的戰友仍在頑抗、國際線也不因人權法通過而休止。我們若想要贏，必須堅持不懈。很多朋友曾詢問我們會否再辦登報，然而香港現時的處境已成國際風眼，無須再藉登報引發世界關注；況且登報花費龐大，亦不應輕率開展。我們期望各位從今天起多用Twitter、多轉發香港的大事，這是我們每個人都可以為國際戰線做的一件事。<br />\n<br />\n最後，團隊寄語各位毋忘721、831等傷疤的同時，也別忘記我們在今夏一起成就過的壯舉；謹記哀痛之餘，多記住628一串數字、記住這個屬於我們全體香港人的G20。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家記得，原來我們也從來未試過如此熱愛香港。<br />\n<br />\nFreedom Hong Kong全體上<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n請各位follow我們的twitter，一同為國際線繼續努力！<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FFreedomHKG&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPCBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=6d114051\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/FreedomHKG</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial/photos/a.340177983324026/446490156026141/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreedomhkgofficial%2Fphotos%2Fa.340177983324026%2F446490156026141%2F&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPCBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=7235057f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/freedomhkgofficial/photos/a.340177983324026/446490156026141/</a>"},{"pid":"5fd6cb3f7b34f21686fa0024f20d6ff4aba468b7","tid":1800687,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c236b5ad13f681e0938cbd4b0352f0f5511bae97","tid":1800687,"uid":185066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"［突發］美國化驗所出左二噁英報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800674\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800674</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3d0777c02778f6494f2896181f936ed961d9e98c","tid":1800687,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c236b5ad13f681e0938c